  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/createml\/mlrandomforestregressor\/modelparameters-swift.struct\/validation\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T13:58:42Z\n---\n\n# validation\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nValidation data.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar validation: MLRandomForestRegressor.ModelParameters.ValidationData { get set }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe default is `.split(strategy: .automatic)`, which automatically generates the validation dataset from 0% to 10% of the training dataset.\n\n## Accessing parameters\n\n- **columnSubsample**: Must be in the range (0, 1).\n- **maxDepth**\n- **maxIterations**\n- **minChildWeight**\n- **minLossReduction**\n- **randomSeed**\n- **rowSubsample**: Must be in the range (0, 1).\n- **validationData**: Validation data represented as a `MLDataTable`.\n\n",
